        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Pull with darkness and then fear.  This is much safer and will prevent the MoB from booking it out of your range.  There is a fear vs undead but not until you advance some more.  Basic fear though should work on everything, just not as well on the undead but it will still work.  Hope this helps some and remember...Dark, Pet, Fear, DoT......It is that simple ;)</P><P>Morgrym Boneblack: Necromancer<BR>Primus Exodus: Veeshan<BR>Evil By Choice:  Being Bad Just Feels To Damn Good<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
